DRE = _____%
```

Based on the DRE result, the system testing and maintenance process can be considered effective if the computed percentage is high. This means that the team was able to detect and correct most errors before the final client acceptance. A lower DRE result would mean that more defects were discovered after deployment, which may require further maintenance and monitoring.

